sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant W as Widget
  participant C as Caddy
  participant API as API
  participant DB as MongoDB
  participant AD as Adapter
  participant P as Provider

  W->>C: POST /conversations/{cid}/messages (Accept: text/event-stream)
  C->>API: reverse_proxy (flush_interval -1)
  API->>API: verify HMAC token bound to cid · validate size · rate-limit per-session and per-IP
  API->>DB: begin_turn — ONE findOneAndUpdate (run lock + append user msg + dedupe key + cap check)
  API-->>W: message.accepted → response.started
  API->>DB: build window (completed, non-empty messages)
  loop up to 5 rounds (last round drops tools)
    API->>AD: send(system prompt, InputItems, tool specs)
    AD->>P: Responses/Messages · stream · store=false · token cap
    P-->>AD: text deltas / tool-call fragments
    AD-->>API: TextDelta / ToolCall / Completed (normalized)
    API-->>W: response.delta{text}
    opt tool call (read-only)
      API->>API: search_knowledge · get_canonical_answer · get_portal_information
    end
  end
  API->>DB: complete_turn (append assistant msg + clear lock)
  API-->>W: response.completed{assistant_message_id, suggested_actions}
